    "title": "Developing trustworthy environmental monitoring data",
    "excerpt": "<p>The Office of Data and Innovation (ODI) built a tool that helps the Department of Water Resources (DWR) create trustworthy environmental monitoring data. Project scope Partner Methods The opportunity DWR collects environmental monitoring data from instruments in water bodies throughout the state. Sometimes, these instruments produce errors or missing values. Anyone with an at-home rain &#8230; <a title=\"Developing trustworthy environmental monitoring data\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/our-work/projects/developing-trustworthy-environmental-monitoring-data/\" aria-label=\"More on Developing trustworthy environmental monitoring data\">Read more</a></p>\n",
